==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cobwork
<hw>Cob"work`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Built of logs, etc.,
laid horizontally, with the ends dovetailed together at the corners, as
in a log house; in marine work, often surrounding a central space filled
with stones; <as>as, a <ex>cobwork</ex> dock or
breakwater</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coca</ent>⟦br⟧
